{"tid":344122,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【玉女大犧牲】有村架純四方面刺激收視 《雛鳥》創開播新高","createTime":"2017-08-02T04:49:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T15:18:17.000Z","uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4aa6ac7e09a475fc38560de2295269681f86196","tid":344122,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:49:47.000Z","msg":"日本純情玉女有村架純深受男士們歡迎，佢增磅為NHK晨早劇《雛鳥》擔任女主角，終於升呢成為國民級女星。有村架純為角色增肥5kg，似乎佢肥晒喺塊面度，搞到佢由包包面變成pizza面，有網民就將有村架純改圖惡搞一番。<br />\n<br />\n《雛鳥》由不少好戲之人參與演出，包括菅野美穗、木村佳乃及澤村一樹等，並帶挈上位男星竹內涼真吸納大批師奶fans，上月26日更錄得開播以來嘅22.2%收視新高。《雛鳥》現時劇情交代到，竹內涼真飾演嘅角色島谷純一郎已同女主角分手，雖然再冇竹內涼真嘅戲份，但就未見影響收視，前日播出嘅第103集，收視都保持住21.8%，估唔到四方面嘅有村架純不單止冇趕客，反而仲深受師奶觀眾支持。<br />\n<br />\n今日，日本方面再公佈《雛鳥》昨日第104集嘅成績，以22.5%創下開播以來最高收視。"},{"pid":"dd3d131f5925f88218fc21039deaee69ae588337","tid":344122,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:51:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170802&amp;guid=57029213&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170802%26guid%3D57029213%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&d=GsAkhMqO7o8lZFzQmfml44zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=cf870c70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170802%26guid%3D57029213%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&h=0c3e0f46\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170802&amp;guid=57029213&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"199fa9cd9d742d1d373c2433670b4192f8876f39","tid":344122,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:53:23.000Z","msg":"我張圖上左報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f89f8be3b041f83ea29c5b00c8bf7c02423345b","tid":344122,"uid":3806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s